Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:26.35,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}I wake once again to a sleepy morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:32.96,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}And carefully fasten my necktie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:39.42,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}As I pass the door to the classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:46.31,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,0)}I walk with my chest held just a little high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:53.44,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,120)}The wind blows through the days spent just like this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:56.93,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I heard it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:01:02.92,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I felt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:06.81,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with these hands that tremble
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:10.19,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,190)}I felt it would happen soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:18.27,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,120)}I watched the millions of stars as they disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:24.78,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,And waved them goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:29.86,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}So happy for them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:35.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu-kun, your report, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:36.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:38.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the Armory's reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,our emergency ammunition stocks will be depleted soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before conducting our next combat operation, we should refill our stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.74,0:01:47.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a new recruit as well, so we'll need new guns too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:48.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:53.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!  Our next operation will be to drop into the Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Drop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:02.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm just... not good with heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?  We're not dropping from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're descending underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhhhh underground, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:13.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,UNDERGROUND?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:15.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it the Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's deep underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have allies there who make weapons for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's there to keep Tenshi from finding out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Guild was seized, our source of ordinance would disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and our odds of success would go way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:32.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:32.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:34.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:35.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Deactivate the traps for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:38.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.  Tonight, it is.  See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go with everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Noda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot's probably just doing whatever he wants again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.27,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't just stand there.  Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:08.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the entrance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we've gone into the Guild, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, someone's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, it's just a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi, huh?  I refuse to accept you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he pick {\i1}here{\i0} to lie in wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:47.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun attaches great significance to situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little cryptic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really {\i1}want{\i0} you to accept me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard... this time won't go the same as the{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Defensive positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The traps aren't deactivated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:08.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what you're seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:13.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The road to the Guild is filled with anti-Angel traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now it looks like they're all activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we forgot to deactivate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.  That's like asking to be annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  The Guild must have rebooted the traps on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:28.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:31.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In {\i1}here{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.97,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wild heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How negligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:38.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait... these Guild guys are doing this even though they know we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you still don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what might happen, we aren't going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, we'll certainly taste the pain of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer to avoid that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the Guild's location is discovered and overtaken,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:54.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,our weapons, ammo, and everything else will cease to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, how would you suggest we fight against Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Guild's decision was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to pursue Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with all the traps activated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:06.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The traps will handle Tenshi somehow... let's retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The traps won't be able to do more than temporarily halt her advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll chase her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, then... what kind of traps are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:32.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All kinds, my friend.  Look forward to 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.  It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.74,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, we're crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In here!  Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Takamatsu-kun's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone but Takamatsu-kun appears unhurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:14.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really alright not to help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll make it out on his own, eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:20.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Up you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:23.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No need for thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:27.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I've grown to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You coming onto me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:29.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx300}- {\fscx100}NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:41.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I forgot!  This is the trap that seals all the exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget something that important!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's about to come is really dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if you touch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:05.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be split in two by the sharpest object imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:06.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Second wave coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You evade it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Third wave coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the third wave, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an X pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do I do with this one!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do {\i1}something{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:27.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open!  Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the sacrifice this time was Matsushita-kun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With a body like that, it's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Man needs to go on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He saw something pretty nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy, right in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:49.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you managed to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, even when you're chopped up like that, you'll still recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The trap's firing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I forgot!  This one's a falling ceiling trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said {\i1}don't{\i0} forget important stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:13.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,TK!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.83,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.  If you go now, you can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.39,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to each other and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'Preciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:24.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even TK sacrificed himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sacrificed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, he'll be fine eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make sure his sacrifice isn't in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I forgooooooooooooot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like I {\i1}said{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Too heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:58.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi and I are gonna fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Don't just decide things yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing everyone here isn't a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!  Hurry up everyone and climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi, can you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:14.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it!  I'm going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!  Don't stop, keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But where do I grab?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever!  Grab wherever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna fall if you grab there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.  What's with her... she smells so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:49.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:56.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hurry up and climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wahhh!  You can't grab there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiooooooot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... um... Hinata was{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He sacrificed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're down to four, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a lot of nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being one of the the few that remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll definitely be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.98,Eyecatch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(853,279)}{\blur1}UTW Presents:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.94,Eyecatch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(853,279)}{\blur1}UTW Presents:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An inundation trap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy... can't even swim, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit's this way.  Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!  Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:07.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What's that doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:18.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:22.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The puppy's gonna get swept away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:24.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san!  No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:35.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up.  It was just a toyyyyyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Shiina-san got sacrificed in one of the traps...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a trap for Tenshi, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:42.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... she couldn't tell at a glance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:46.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute things are her weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:49.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.  That's unexpectedly cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she'll be alright too, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:10.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were a real unit, we'd have been completely wiped out by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a terrible leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are anti-Angel traps after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:19.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can't even stop us, what good are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:30.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.  We need to dry our clothes, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:35.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed that you're able to lead a group like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you selected as the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I was the first to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:41.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Against Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:47.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:50.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about what you don't have.  Memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:53.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The time when you were alive... before this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:54.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Including me, four siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:01.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the eldest daughter, and had two younger sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and one younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:08.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My parent's work was going well, so we were quite well-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:12.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were surrounded by nature, so it was almost like living in a villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was during Summer Vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:20.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the afternoon, when my parents were out, some men I'd never seen before were in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:24.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was the middle of Summer, they were wearing stifling-looking balaclavas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew they'd come to do something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:32.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the eldest daughter, so I thought I definitely had to protect my siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... no way that would happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:40.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, the guys were after our valuables...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:43.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But they couldn't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:48.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they started indiscriminately destroying\Nwindowpanes and televisions, and getting angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:54.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, they came up with the worst thing to do to us siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl, you're the eldest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents must've told you where the valuables are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:05.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "if there's an earthquake, grab these and run",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or "if robbers come, give them these and ask them to leave".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your parents must've told you something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:18.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, go and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:25.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't like what you find, we'll have to do something bad to these kids, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got 10 minutes apiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and find something good within 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:34.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I started searching the house frantically.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:35.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My head was pounding like it was about to split.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:38.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was nauseous.  I was ready to faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:41.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My siblings' lives were on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:43.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to find something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:47.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I had no idea what sort of valuables they were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:51.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, it's time.  I have to hurry.  I have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the biggest-looking thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just bring this down, I'm sure it's worth a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:19.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time the police arrived... 30 minutes had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one alive... was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I care if I'm reincarnated as a water flea, or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:34.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that if God exists... I want to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:37.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... it's just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:40.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't intervene when bad things happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:45.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That afternoon, I truly thought I was a responsible older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:49.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, everything I wanted to protect was taken from me in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't find that unreasonable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't find a life like that unforgivable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had memories like that, I'd want to just sit back and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're fighting, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:12.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you die, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:19.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.  It wasn't suicide or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who commited suicide wouldn't fight back like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:24.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, there's no suicides in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Guild?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys make weapons here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:12.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to make your way here past all those traps, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have known you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, where's Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:18.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her advance was halted recently, but it seems she's begun to move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:29.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:34.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're abandoning this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:36.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're fine with not being able to make weapons anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important isn't places or tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:42.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you guys forgotten that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:50.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, nothing with a soul can be given life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only objects of form can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:57.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you know the composition and structure of the object,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that's essentially all you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even make things out of mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we eventually prioritized efficiency, and all we do now is make replicas in this factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:11.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy's a high-schooler, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:16.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though in the past, we used to breath life into objects using only the shape and memory of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go to the Old Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been left alone for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking to create things from Earth, there's a mountain's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to get back to the surface from there, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll blow it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:32.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, Tenshi could cross over to the Old Guild from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:35.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only place we have left to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:45.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to bring with you are your\Nmemories and your pride as a craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong, you guys!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!  Prepare the explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see some teamwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:55.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no traps left.  Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To buy us time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:18.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you came.  Aren't you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I stayed down there, there's nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's responding too quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:55.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.  She can keep up with her in close combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Load shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:58.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to fire with her up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:04.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!  Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:20.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:29.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, you get things done when you need to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that doesn't look easy to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-kun, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:45.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands brace for impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRE!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:53.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cannon blew up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:59.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch... I guess you can't make something you don't have memories of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:00.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make things you don't know how to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:02.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi's waking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something with these!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shell-squad, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:14.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All members accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.  We'll blow the Guild up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:18.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:41.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:43.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This place really is empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:45.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:48.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tear down the walls, you'll have all the earth you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:49.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a crappy nesting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.65,0:21:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you to make a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:52.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get started, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey morons, you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We tore down the Guild, and blew up Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the Old Guild, and let everyone know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:11.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll replenish our arms as fast as we can, before Tenshi recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.13,0:22:13.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All members, to the Old Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:15.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat:  Hurry up, morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saved her without even thinking twice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:24.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that if God exists, I want to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:28.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... it's just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:30.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)}It's too terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:34.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:36.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, this is why everyone follows you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:40.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You truly are a leader.{\i0}
