Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:53.30,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I've always walked alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:23:00.69,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}When I turned around, everyone was far away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:08.34,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Even so, I walked on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:14.24,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}That's what it was to be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:21.88,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm not afraid of anything anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:30.68,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}That's what I try to tell myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:41.73,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Eventually, everyone will be alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:49.49,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}They'll continue to live only through their memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:57.20,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Rather than try to love and laugh at this loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:24:03.75,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will fight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:10.97,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will never show you my tears
