Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c6] Why is the new song a ballad?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:19.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c37] Please, call me Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.69,0:24:20.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c83] ... I couldn't sing the song I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:20.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c76] It was an incredible fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c40] This is Tenshi's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.53,0:24:24.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c62D] What's gonna get exciting later, is... Alchemy!　Alchemy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.35,0:24:22.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c330] Well then, what do {\i1}you{\i0} think happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c118] No memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:24.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c219] Tenshi has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.65,0:24:25.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c167] Just when I was starting to have a better opinion of you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:25.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c231] ... That's as far as you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:24.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c326] The worst possible situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:29.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c245] ... Also, {\i1}don't touch it{\i0}!
